WEBVTT

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:31.360
drifting from town to town
for over 30 years.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.480
A broad coalition

00:06:34.320 --> 00:06:36.176
of social service agencies,

00:06:36.200 --> 00:06:37.616
funders and designers,

00:06:37.640 --> 00:06:39.720
created this place.

00:06:41.200 --> 00:06:45.336
Each 400 square foot cottage
is designed beautifully

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:46.560
as a permanent home.

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:50.016
Gregory now has a key

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:51.496
to a door

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:52.936
to his own house.

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:56.216
He describes the sense
of security that it brings him.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:07:00.216
Something he had lived without
for three decades.